
Add workflow-init skill for scaffolding Vercel Workflow
Introduces a /workflow-init slash command so durable multi-step tasks
(catalog resync, bulk email, Shopify reconciliations) can be scaffolded
against @vercel/workflow with the repo's conventions baked in — typed
workflow file, route handler, vercel.json entry, and the security
guardrails around service-role keys and signing secrets.

